## Architecture Requirements (Ratatui demo style)

### Feature flags for backends (like demo)

Support:

* default feature: `crossterm`
* optional: `termion`
* optional: `termwiz`

Commands must work:

* `cargo run --release`
* `cargo run --release --no-default-features --features=termion`
* `cargo run --release --no-default-features --features=termwiz`

### Suggested crate structure (required)

```
src/
  main.rs
  app.rs
  tui.rs
  event.rs
  ui/
    mod.rs
    overview.rs
    rpc_mix.rs
