    proc_net_tcp.txt
    proc_net_tcp6.txt
```

### Dependencies (keep tight)

* `ratatui`
* backend crates: `crossterm` (default) / `termion` / `termwiz` under features
* `clap`
* `anyhow` or `thiserror` for errors
* Avoid tokio; use threads + channels (std) unless truly needed

